These instructions include the dates of the registration period during which you will be able to enter. 


Время в EDT (Eastern Daylight Time) на 7 часов отстает от времени в Москве.
Время в EST (Eastern Standard Time) на 8 часов отстает от времени в MSK.


4. Как долго проверять, выиграл ли ты.
2021 Entrant Status Check begin on June 6, 2020.
Entrants should keep their confirmation number until at least September 30, 2021


